author: Dennis M. Stutzenburg
title: Dennis M. Stutzenburg
text: It may be that people just rate the companies with the highest score. But it is my way to give a good job to a company! I have given this 5 star for the fast service and easy purchase process! I have to say another thing, I would defiantly purchase from TackleDirect and I do mention them on FB and plus my friends!
